    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question. my doctor just gave me a prescription for clarithromycin for a sinus infection i have. i also take simvastatin for my cholesterol every night. is it okay to take both of these at the same time or do i need to wait a few hours between them?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
